Write a program to enter even numbers with array size 30 elements using functions inside a class and display the result.

Write a program to enter same value into array size 10 elements using functions inside a class and display the result.

Write a program
a. Take 2 arrays of different size.
b. Enter the values to both the arrays using single function
c. Compare both the array values at each index
d. Display the values present at index of both arrays.
e. Display the number of elements matched in the array [count].

Design an ALU inside a class.
a. Write program to perform operations [+ - * /] and display result using Scope Resolution Operator.

Write a Program and Display
a. Take 2 Queues in a class
b. Enter the values into 2 Queues using “THIS” operator.
c. Print both Queues.
d. Do Push front and pushback value operation using FUNCTION and THIS operator.
